Package: checklist
Title: Check the Structure of Student Assignment Submissions
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Colin",
           family = "Rundel",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rundel@gmail.com")
Description: Tools for instructors to check the structure and
    reproducibility of student project and assignment submissions.
    Includes checks for required, allowed, or disallowed files and
    package dependencies, and that 'R Markdown' and 'Quarto'
    documents render successfully.
